Acclaimed actor Kyle MacLachlan talks about taking his son to the Super Bowl, interviewing young people on his podcast, and the fan frenzy around his hit show, "Fallout." Season two of "Fallout" is streaming now on Prime Video and new episodes of the "What Are We Even Doing?" podcast drop on Thursdays wherever you get your podcasts.
